snippet.title: Skyclimbers - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Cross-Platform Multiplayer City-Building RPG developed by Paratope

Learn more: https://skyclimbers.net/

Build your kingdom, choose your class, and tame monsters in this City-Building RPG that takes place in a procedurally generated anime-themed universe. 

S T E A M https://store.steampowered.com/app/1362000/Skyclimbers/

D I S C O R D https://discord.gg/skyclimbers

S U B R E D D I T https://www.reddit.com/r/PlaySkyclimbers/

T W I T T E R  https://twitter.com/playskyclimbers
